name: Twisted DeathMatchs DeathMatchs 3
description: This is New collection of 4 Deathmatchs that consists of ALL types of layouts. Each level is unique in it's own way, with each one having an outside area. These levels are made for intense FRAG action! All the levels contain ALL or MOST of the weapons. No secret areas, everything is accessable, or triggered with a switch, or teleport.
